comments: Excellent conference! The keynote speakers were inspirational and the workshops provided practical skills I can immediately apply. The venue was perfect and staff were very helpful.
Very good content and organization. Some sessions were too crowded, but overall a worthwhile experience. Networking opportunities were excellent.
Great content focused on modern web development techniques. Would have appreciated more advanced sessions, but the fundamentals were well covered.
Content was good but the WiFi was spotty which impacted some of the hands-on workshop experiences. Otherwise well organized.
